  "description": {
    "zh": "天气真美，不是吗？完美地享受外面的新鲜空气，如果不是那些坐在塔楼和屋顶上的混蛋，这些讨厌的家伙……真该有人让他们付出代价！\n\n我的一些员工发誓说AK配上PSO-1瞄准镜好用，这儿的“炒作”是怎么回事？真的很值得怀疑，我不认为这完全是一种有效的战术，嗯，我想只有一种方法能找出答案。而且我正在寻找一些新步枪，所以你何不给我造一把呢？确保它有带眼罩的BelOMO瞄准镜，安全第一！我会给你写下所有细节，我也可以把武器的机匣给你，你觉得你能做到吗？\n\nAK-74M 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于275\n - 重量小于4.5公斤\n - 人机工效50或更高\n - 耐久度高于60%\n - 弹匣容量45发或更多\n - PSO瞄准镜眼罩",
    "en": "Beautiful day, isn't it? Perfect to enjoy the fresh air outside, if only there wouldn't be those assholes sitting on towers and rooftops, these annoying fucks... Someone should really make them pay!\n\nSome of my staff swears on AKs with the PSO-1 scope, what's the \"hype\" about here? It's really questionable, I don't think it's exactly an effective tactic, well I guess there's only one way to find out. Besides I'm looking for some new rifles, so how about you build me one? Make sure it has the BelOMO scope with an eyecup, safety first! I'll write you down all the details, I can give you the receiver of the weapon too, you think you can do that?\n\nAK-74M Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 275\n - Weight less than 4.5 KG\n - Ergonomics 50 or higher\n - Durability higher than 60 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 45 or more\n - PSO Scope Eyecup"
  },
